{
  "texts": [
    "As the code is multipurpose, it does not have any predefined boundary condition, and it is the user's responsibility to treat the boundaries according to the particular setup.",
    "For efficient usage of the computational resources several numerical schemes are implemented in MANCHA3D.",
    "By default, the governing Eqs.",
    "46 -49 are evolved by means of a memory-saving variant of the explicit Runge-Kutta (RK) scheme.",
    "3 Two more integration schemes can be used to deal with the nonideal terms in the energy and induction equations, Eqs. 48 and 49."
  ]
}